ael Kremer">Kremer</a> (2019)</span>&#160;<span class="sep-liste">·</span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Paul_Milgrom" title="Paul Milgrom">Milgrom</a>, <a href="/wiki/Robert_B._Wilson" title="Robert B. Wilson">Wilson</a> (2020)</span></td>
